column4: Huawei  Intel expand tie-up amid China's rising scrutiny of U.S. tech firms
column5: BEIJING China's Huawei Technologies Co Ltd [HWT.UL] and Intel Corp are expanding an existing alliance to provide cloud computing to global telecoms carriers  as U.S. tech firms vie for Chinese tie-ups to retain access to a tough mainland market.
